 of cusp forms that is the main\norganizational principle since the 60s, and in it the building blocks are the\ncuspidal representations which are, in some sense, the \"LARGEST\".\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 23 May 2021 21:52:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-05-25"}
